    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Sika India - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "We at Sika India are looking for an experienced Manufacturing Engineer based out of Rajkot. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Sika India:\nSika India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sika India!",
